OL,3,C1 in 5 drinkers in Wales putting their
OL,4,Chealth at 'serious risk', charity warns
OL,6,FOne in five drinkers in Wales are
OL,7,Fputting their health at "serious
OL,8,Frisk", a charity has warned.
OL,10,FAlmost a quarter (22%) of drinkers
OL,11,Fsurveyed in Wales are exceeding the UK
OL,12,Fchief medical officers' low-risk
OL,13,Fdrinking guidelines.
OL,15,FThat's according to a new survey by
OL,16,FDrinkaware, a charity aiming to reduce
OL,17,Falcohol harm.
OL,19,FThis is higher than the level for all
OL,20,FUK drinkers (19%), equivalent to
OL,21,Falmost half a million people in Wales.
