OL,3,C1 in 5 drinkers in Wales putting their
OL,4,Chealth at 'serious risk', charity warns
OL,6,FIt found that 30% of people in Wales
OL,7,Fsaid they were concerned about someone
OL,8,Felse's drinking in the last year.
OL,10,FThe survey also found that alcohol
OL,11,Fmoderation is on the increase, with
OL,12,Falmost nine in 10 (89%) drinkers in
OL,13,FWales moderating their drinking in
OL,14,Fsome way ` up from 85% in 2018.
OL,16,FTaking drink-free days was the most
OL,17,Fpopular way to moderate in 2024.
